{"tid":766920,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得香港既地鐵/火車其實好安全？","createTime":"2018-08-04T04:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T19:02:39.000Z","uid":36296,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b1b418ed5aa68d01da9725fab7cf32b0807a4eda","tid":766920,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:43:58.000Z","msg":"唔係講緊列車安全 係講緊治安<br />\n係香港搭左咁多年都唔會覺得有危險 唔計縱火個單既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但歐洲美國 甚至澳洲 車上邊真係乜人都有 道友 白mk 黑mk 紋曬身既醉酒佬 racist white trash  <br />\n<br />\n每次搭車都要揀個安全既位 其實都幾恐佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739be0abd478b27d641e89e36bd6d95085e46158","tid":766920,"uid":151324,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:47:38.000Z","msg":"係 應該學大陸咁每個站都要過機檢查"},{"pid":"122792da49abf59a1b4a4e4e0f1e46595bf6ea15","tid":766920,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c14d9e8d34eb92a5603a6268cba698c22c1dac","tid":766920,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":28,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:48:57.000Z","msg":"係好安全<br />\n唔計縱火果單 唔計排隊比人打到爆曬肛 唔計廢老大戰南亞狗 唔計港女比人偷拍 唔計地鐵電梯成日斷<br />\n真係好安全既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdda5506789356b03520d563d654e74065125944","tid":766920,"uid":81387,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:49:40.000Z","msg":"逼到冇位做危險野 實安全啦"},{"pid":"2877fdb38af5b66ed7548c0152db694da1b1090b","tid":766920,"uid":172024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:51:02.000Z","msg":"整體黎講香港治安係世界唔知第幾位 都算係咁啦～"},{"pid":"a2630312d1f902b79bcae4cb8fab843b81c930ec","tid":766920,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fdda5506789356b03520d563d654e74065125944","tid":766920,"uid":81387,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20